tafsir[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"Min tellinii Quraana e na tonnga faade e kammu ɓurɗo ɓadaade hono no Min puɗɗorno tellide mbo e Annabi-yo o his- e jemma leylatul qadiri nder lewru koorko."
  97,2,"Mbela ana anndi-aan nelaaɗo- ko woni e hembo e moƴƴere e barke?"
  97,3,"O jemma mawdo moƴƴere, ɓuri ujnere lewru moƴƴude sabu ko woni e hembo e iimaan e fawaade e Alla."
  97,4,"Malaukaaji na telloo jibriil kadi telloo heen e sakkitoore joom mum en Ceniiɗo e kala yamiroore nde Alla ñaawi e ndeen hitaande foti ko arsuka wolla maayde wolla jibinegol eka nanndi heen."
  97,5,"O jemma barkinaaɗo ko mbo moƴƴere kammba fof gila arwannde haa sakket hembo haa feeral wenndoogo."
